ility of human leadership? </div><div class="t m289 x92 h4 y30 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Verses 6, 7, 10, 11, </div><div class="t m2b6 x18 h4 y2027 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3. </div><div class="t m1ab x61 h4 yc73 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Who were associated with Moses in this responsibility? Micah 6:4. </div><div class="t m179c x26 h3a yb67 ff4 fs1a fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">NOTE.—&quot;Aaron </div><div class="t m723 x6c h4 yca ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and Miriam had occupied a position of high honor and </div><div class="t m8bc x92 h4 y6c4 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">leadership in Israel. Both were endowed with the prophetic gift, and both had </div><div class="t m3da x92 h4 ya3c ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">been divinely associated with Moses in the deliverance of the Hebrews. &apos;I sent </div><div class="t m2920 x2e h84 y1af ff2 fs1e fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">[</div><div class="t m2236 x2f h4 y1af ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">7</div><div class="t m19aa x3b h84 y1af ff2 fs1e fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">] </div><div class="t m2a0d x2a h84 y45a ff2 fs1e fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"> </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
